<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/consumer-council-for-water> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Consumer Council for Water (CCW) represents water and sewerage consumers in England and Wales and takes up unresolved complaints. CCW is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department for Environment, Food & Rural Affairs ."@en .
